1
00:00:17,726 --> 00:00:19,519
HONG MIN-BEOM

2
00:00:19,602 --> 00:00:20,770
Gang-yong?

3
00:00:20,854 --> 00:00:22,397
Beri saya sepuluh minit.

4
00:00:22,480 --> 00:00:23,314
Pengarah Hong.

5
00:00:23,398 --> 00:00:24,858
Jangan putuskan talian.

6
00:00:25,734 --> 00:00:27,193
Terbalikkan telefon.

7
00:00:27,277 --> 00:00:29,487
Supaya saya boleh dengar. Awak faham?

8
00:00:39,414 --> 00:00:40,749
Saya takkan berkias.

9
00:00:43,001 --> 00:00:43,918
Apa ini?

10
00:00:49,674 --> 00:00:51,926
Jangan merengek, duduk diam.

11
00:00:52,010 --> 00:00:53,178
GANG-YONG

12
00:00:53,261 --> 00:00:54,095
Kau dengar?

13
00:00:54,179 --> 00:00:56,431
Jahanam. Apa kau kata?

14
00:00:56,514 --> 00:00:57,932
Kau tak sayang nyawa?

15
00:00:59,434 --> 00:01:02,145
Hoi, samseng! Kau buat kesilapan besar.

16
00:01:02,812 --> 00:01:03,730
Suruh dia diam.

17
00:01:05,398 --> 00:01:06,232
Gang-yong.

18
00:01:06,775 --> 00:01:07,609
Diam!

19
00:01:07,692 --> 00:01:09,819
Kau akan meringkuk dalam penjara!

20
00:01:09,903 --> 00:01:10,779
Celaka!

21
00:01:12,405 --> 00:01:14,949
Hoi, celaka! Baik awak senyap!

22
00:01:18,286 --> 00:01:19,120
Bodoh.

23
00:01:21,873 --> 00:01:22,832
Dah bertenang?

24
00:01:25,627 --> 00:01:26,669
Tak nak jawab?

25
00:01:27,879 --> 00:01:29,005
Kau nak apa?

26
00:01:29,631 --> 00:01:32,425
Polis Yeongmoonpo akan terima
satu laporan.

27
00:01:33,134 --> 00:01:34,385
Lelaki bermotosikal

28
00:01:34,469 --> 00:01:37,347
mengelar leher mangsa di parkir
dan larikan diri.

29
00:01:38,014 --> 00:01:39,057
Ambil nombor ini.

30
00:01:39,808 --> 00:01:41,893
Seoul, Gangdong, A.

31
00:01:41,976 --> 00:01:44,312
Enam, empat, tiga, lapan.

32
00:01:45,146 --> 00:01:47,690
Itu plat nombor. Tentu tiada dalam sistem.

33
00:01:48,525 --> 00:01:50,527
Jejaki lokasi yang dia tujui.

34
00:01:52,320 --> 00:01:53,571
Hei, untuk jejaki…

35
00:01:53,655 --> 00:01:55,365
Aku tahu. Susah dan ambil masa.

36
00:01:56,032 --> 00:01:57,242
Sebab itu aku suruh kau.

37
00:01:58,201 --> 00:01:59,994
Sudah pukul 10. Kau ada lima jam.

38
00:02:00,537 --> 00:02:01,496
Kalau tak jumpa,

39
00:02:03,456 --> 00:02:06,251
pertunjukan bogel sepupu kau
akan tersebar.

40
00:02:06,334 --> 00:02:09,045
Sama juga jika kau cuba buat helah.

41
00:02:09,712 --> 00:02:12,841
Kalau tak nak tengok
harga saham Iil jatuh esok pagi…

42
00:02:13,341 --> 00:02:14,175
Laksanakan.

43
00:02:18,596 --> 00:02:19,430
Apa nombornya?

44
00:02:20,181 --> 00:02:21,349
735629.

45
00:02:29,440 --> 00:02:30,275
Jumpa lagi.

46
00:02:34,487 --> 00:02:35,947
Celaka!

47
00:03:07,228 --> 00:03:10,607
BLOODHOUNDS

48
00:03:17,155 --> 00:03:18,239
Helo.

49
00:03:18,323 --> 00:03:20,200
- Mari sini.
- Tabik!

50
00:03:20,283 --> 00:03:21,117
Ceh.

51
00:03:21,743 --> 00:03:22,994
Saya belanja soju.

52
00:03:30,168 --> 00:03:31,002
Di sini.

53
00:03:31,085 --> 00:03:32,128
Terima kasih.

54
00:03:32,712 --> 00:03:33,671
- Helo.
- Hai.

55
00:03:36,007 --> 00:03:37,926
Mayat direbus beberapa hari

56
00:03:38,509 --> 00:03:40,011
sehingga tulang lembut.

57
00:03:40,094 --> 00:03:42,430
Kemudian dikisar dan ditabur ke laut.

58
00:03:42,513 --> 00:03:44,557
Satu mayat, 15 juta won.

59
00:03:44,641 --> 00:03:46,184
Kita takkan jumpa apa-apa.

60
00:03:46,976 --> 00:03:49,145
Mereka rebus orang? Gila betul.

61
00:03:49,729 --> 00:03:50,730
Siapa beritahu awak?

62
00:03:51,606 --> 00:03:52,982
Saya jumpa Seung-deok.

63
00:03:53,066 --> 00:03:55,193
Dia dalam penjara. Bagaimana dia tahu?

64
00:03:55,276 --> 00:03:57,862
Penjara tempat paling mudah
untuk dapatkan maklumat.

65
00:03:59,113 --> 00:04:00,698
Hei, kamu okey?

66
00:04:01,616 --> 00:04:02,992
- Okey.
- Okey.

67
00:04:03,576 --> 00:04:05,536
Tentu kamu terkejut saksikan hal tadi.

68
00:04:07,747 --> 00:04:08,581
Tapi,

69
00:04:09,207 --> 00:04:11,626
apa jadi jika kasino itu beroperasi?

70
00:04:11,709 --> 00:04:12,543
Apa jadi?

71
00:04:13,878 --> 00:04:15,588
Myeong-gil akan kaut untung.

72
00:04:15,672 --> 00:04:16,881
- Begitu.
- Gun-woo.

73
00:04:17,507 --> 00:04:18,341
Ya.

74
00:04:18,424 --> 00:04:22,428
Ramai penagih dan kaki judi
yang buat pinjaman dengan lintah darat.

75
00:04:22,512 --> 00:04:25,390
Myeong-gil akan gabungkan
kasino dengan pinjaman.

76
00:04:26,015 --> 00:04:27,850
Semakin ramai pelanggan kasino,

77
00:04:28,351 --> 00:04:30,478
jumlah peminjam juga akan meningkat.

78
00:04:30,561 --> 00:04:32,981
Kesimpulannya, ia keuntungan mudah.

79
00:04:33,940 --> 00:04:35,984
Tapi, kasino untuk warga asing.

80
00:04:37,568 --> 00:04:38,820
Awak rasa dia peduli?

81
00:04:38,903 --> 00:04:39,737
Oh…

82
00:04:40,405 --> 00:04:42,198
Kaki judi besar bermain secara haram.

83
00:04:42,699 --> 00:04:44,075
Itu cara untuk untung.

84
00:04:45,451 --> 00:04:47,078
Apabila dana dah mencukupi,

85
00:04:47,787 --> 00:04:49,289
dia akan beli bangunan.

86
00:04:49,372 --> 00:04:53,668
Kemudian dia akan cagarkan untuk
pinjaman pembelian bangunan lebih besar.

87
00:04:55,128 --> 00:04:56,713
Penyangak yang hebat.

88
00:04:56,796 --> 00:04:58,089
Untuk bayar hutang,

89
00:04:58,172 --> 00:05:00,258
lebih banyak duit perlu masuk ke kasino.

90
00:05:00,341 --> 00:05:03,177
Smile Capital akan jerut
lebih ramai mangsa.

91
00:05:03,761 --> 00:05:05,763
Kim Myeong-gil akan berkuasa.

92
00:05:18,192 --> 00:05:20,611
Duit datuk yang Myeong-gil curi dulu

93
00:05:21,404 --> 00:05:23,364
berjumlah lebih 20 bilion won.

94
00:05:23,865 --> 00:05:26,284
Jika kita berjaya dapatkannya semula,

95
00:05:26,367 --> 00:05:29,412
apa kata kita ke luar negara
bersama Gun-woo dan Woo-jin?

96
00:05:30,955 --> 00:05:33,082
Duit yang ada pun dah cukup.

97
00:05:35,084 --> 00:05:35,918
Betul, tapi,

98
00:05:36,919 --> 00:05:38,671
tak boleh ke luar negara sebab COVID.

99
00:05:40,840 --> 00:05:41,674
Betul…

100
00:05:43,634 --> 00:05:44,635
Jom ke Rom.

101
00:05:47,555 --> 00:05:48,556
Kenapa Rom?

102
00:05:48,639 --> 00:05:51,893
Waktu datuk 20 tahun,
datuk tonton filem Roman Holiday.

103
00:05:52,977 --> 00:05:55,521
Datuk nekad untuk ke sana
apabila banyak duit,

104
00:05:55,605 --> 00:05:57,398
tapi masih tak kesampaian.

105
00:05:57,940 --> 00:05:59,734
Datuk fikir tentu seronok

106
00:06:00,735 --> 00:06:01,611
jika pergi

107
00:06:02,195 --> 00:06:03,863
bersama kamu bertiga.

108
00:06:07,742 --> 00:06:09,827
Cakap sahaja, datuk akan belikan.

109
00:06:10,912 --> 00:06:14,040
Datuk, Itali penuh dengan barang mahal.

110
00:06:14,123 --> 00:06:15,541
Ia negara barang mewah.

111
00:06:15,625 --> 00:06:16,667
Budak bertuah.

112
00:06:17,460 --> 00:06:18,669
Ini Choi Tae-ho.

113
00:06:19,796 --> 00:06:21,672
Datuk akan tunjuk cara berbelanja.

114
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:26,803
Datuk, itu dipanggil "flex."

115
00:06:28,054 --> 00:06:28,888
Okey.

116
00:06:29,555 --> 00:06:31,391
Datuk akan tunjuk cara "flex."

117
00:06:32,850 --> 00:06:34,102
Tak perlu tunjuk.

118
00:06:34,185 --> 00:06:36,020
Cakap sahaja "flex."

119
00:06:38,064 --> 00:06:38,940
"Flex."

120
00:06:44,404 --> 00:06:46,447
Kita selesaikan hal ini dulu

121
00:06:47,323 --> 00:06:48,282
dan pergi bersama.

122
00:07:04,757 --> 00:07:05,591
Bos.

123
00:07:06,884 --> 00:07:08,094
Okey, baiklah.

124
00:07:09,345 --> 00:07:10,179
Baiklah.

125
00:07:11,180 --> 00:07:14,392
Yang-jung, bos ajak
kita minum di rumah dia.

126
00:07:16,519 --> 00:07:17,937
Nampaknya, dia gembira.

127
00:07:19,605 --> 00:07:20,773
Kamu minum?

128
00:07:21,941 --> 00:07:22,775
Tentu sekali!

129
00:08:18,164 --> 00:08:19,373
Boleh cepatkan?

130
00:08:19,957 --> 00:08:21,834
Dua atau empat kali kelajuan?

131
00:08:21,918 --> 00:08:23,252
- Dua.
- Baiklah.

132
00:08:30,593 --> 00:08:32,053
Jika saya Myeong-gil,

133
00:08:32,637 --> 00:08:35,681
saya anggap Im Jang-do
dah dedahkan kelemahan saya

134
00:08:35,765 --> 00:08:38,434
dan pindahkan pemacu keras
ke tempat selamat.

135
00:08:39,936 --> 00:08:41,354
Awak rasa dia ada masa?

136
00:08:41,854 --> 00:08:44,899
Kita dah lumpuhkan tangan dan kaki dia.

137
00:08:44,982 --> 00:08:46,859
Selain orang bernama En. Jung,

138
00:08:46,943 --> 00:08:48,569
dia tak boleh harapkan sesiapa.

139
00:08:49,362 --> 00:08:50,196
Lagipun,

140
00:08:51,155 --> 00:08:53,824
dia takkan kongsi
maklumat sewenang-wenangnya.

141
00:08:55,368 --> 00:08:56,827
Tak perlu sorok pun.

142
00:08:57,411 --> 00:08:59,413
Dia boleh letak dalam but.
Kita takkan tahu.

143
00:09:00,164 --> 00:09:01,541
Dia sedar tentang itu.

144
00:09:02,291 --> 00:09:03,125
Betul.

145
00:09:04,418 --> 00:09:07,255
Jika kita berjaya pengaruhi musuh dia,

146
00:09:07,338 --> 00:09:08,798
kita boleh menang.

147
00:09:11,425 --> 00:09:13,553
Sebab itu pemacu keras itu penting.

148
00:09:14,053 --> 00:09:17,390
Ia pasti mengandungi
banyak maklumat mangsa ugut Myeong-gil.

149
00:09:18,099 --> 00:09:20,560
Motif mereka sama dengan kita.

150
00:09:22,019 --> 00:09:24,230
Tentu ada ramai individu berkuasa,

151
00:09:24,313 --> 00:09:26,399
seperti anak sulung Kumpulan Iil.

152
00:09:29,110 --> 00:09:31,821
Jika berlarutan, tak bermanfaat buat kita.

153
00:09:32,488 --> 00:09:35,741
Tentu Myeong-gil dah sebarkan
pengaruh dia.

154
00:09:36,367 --> 00:09:38,369
Pasti dia dah rasuah pihak polis,

155
00:09:39,161 --> 00:09:39,996
pendakwa,

156
00:09:40,705 --> 00:09:42,039
dan ahli-ahli politik.

157
00:09:42,748 --> 00:09:45,668
Bahaya jika kita leka walau sesaat.

158
00:09:46,627 --> 00:09:47,545
Betul.

159
00:09:47,628 --> 00:09:50,756
Kita berjaya jatuhkan
tiga pengikut dia, bukan?

160
00:09:51,882 --> 00:09:52,717
Ya.

161
00:09:53,718 --> 00:09:56,262
Jika fikir terlalu jauh, kita pasti risau.

162
00:09:56,887 --> 00:09:59,599
Tapi saya rasa, setakat ini semua okey.

163
00:09:59,682 --> 00:10:01,225
Tiada siapa yang cedera.

164
00:10:01,892 --> 00:10:02,727
Betul.

165
00:10:03,561 --> 00:10:05,271
Kita buat satu persatu.

166
00:10:05,354 --> 00:10:06,647
Kita jatuhkan Kim,

167
00:10:07,148 --> 00:10:08,274
kemudian, syarikat dia.

168
00:10:09,025 --> 00:10:10,067
Lagipun,

169
00:10:10,151 --> 00:10:11,777
tanpa Im Jang-do dan Kim Jun-min,

170
00:10:12,278 --> 00:10:14,530
tentu Kim sedang kecut perut.

171
00:10:17,158 --> 00:10:18,951
Betul juga.

172
00:10:20,828 --> 00:10:21,746
Jadi…

173
00:10:24,540 --> 00:10:26,292
Oh, ya.

174
00:10:26,876 --> 00:10:28,169
Tuan bertiga.

175
00:10:30,921 --> 00:10:33,549
Saya ingin buat minum ucap selamat

176
00:10:34,050 --> 00:10:36,135
demi keselamatan dan matlamat kita.

177
00:10:36,802 --> 00:10:40,014
Apabila saya cakap,
"Ayuh cari pemacu keras,"

178
00:10:40,097 --> 00:10:42,266
sambut dengan, "Kim Myeong-gil nahas."

179
00:10:43,184 --> 00:10:45,186
Sambut dengan kuat.

180
00:10:45,269 --> 00:10:47,355
Saya akan mulakan. Angkat gelas.

181
00:10:49,899 --> 00:10:51,692
Ayuh cari pemacu keras. Kim Myeong-gil…

182
00:10:51,776 --> 00:10:53,569
- Nahas!
- Nahas!

183
00:11:44,787 --> 00:11:46,455
Saya sedang ke Balai Polis Joongang.

184
00:11:46,539 --> 00:11:48,874
Mereka ke Joongang-gu dari Dongpa-gu.

185
00:11:50,084 --> 00:11:51,836
Boleh cari sebelum jam tiga?

186
00:11:52,837 --> 00:11:54,797
Boleh, jika mereka berhenti di sana,

187
00:11:54,880 --> 00:11:56,507
tapi jika mereka ke daerah lain,

188
00:11:57,174 --> 00:11:58,551
saya kena teruskan.

189
00:12:00,261 --> 00:12:01,095
Tolonglah.

190
00:12:01,721 --> 00:12:03,097
Jangan risau.

191
00:12:03,180 --> 00:12:05,641
Buat masa ini, kita patuh sahaja.

192
00:12:06,600 --> 00:12:09,979
Selepas kes ini, saya akan cari
jalan supaya dia ditangkap.

193
00:12:10,855 --> 00:12:11,731
Terima kasih.

194
00:12:12,314 --> 00:12:13,399
Min-beom.

195
00:12:13,482 --> 00:12:16,277
Awak fikir saya akan biar
dia ganggu keluarga kita?

196
00:12:17,570 --> 00:12:18,404
Jangan risau.

197
00:12:18,487 --> 00:12:19,572
Okey?

198
00:12:19,655 --> 00:12:21,073
Saya harapkan awak sahaja.

199
00:12:21,824 --> 00:12:24,034
Jangan minum banyak sangat, okey?

200
00:12:24,910 --> 00:12:25,786
Okey.

201
00:12:46,515 --> 00:12:49,226
Kenapa tak kawal jika tak pandai minum?

202
00:12:49,310 --> 00:12:50,352
Saya rasa,

203
00:12:51,312 --> 00:12:52,772
dia gembira.

204
00:12:52,855 --> 00:12:54,815
Saya mengantuk. Awak?

205
00:12:54,899 --> 00:12:56,400
Saya nak turun semula.

206
00:12:56,484 --> 00:12:58,235
- Tak penat?
- Tak, saya okey.

207
00:13:01,947 --> 00:13:02,782
Syabas.

208
00:13:02,865 --> 00:13:03,699
Ya.

209
00:13:10,122 --> 00:13:10,956
Gun-woo.

210
00:13:12,416 --> 00:13:13,250
Gun-woo.

211
00:13:15,419 --> 00:13:16,253
Belum tidur?

212
00:13:17,505 --> 00:13:18,923
Belum. Kenapa tak tidur?

213
00:13:19,006 --> 00:13:21,008
Kami sedang minum di bawah.

214
00:13:21,675 --> 00:13:23,928
- Awak juga?
- Taklah.

215
00:13:26,722 --> 00:13:28,933
Mak akan masakkan sup untuk sarapan.

216
00:13:29,016 --> 00:13:30,935
Okey. Tidurlah. Saya tutup pintu.

217
00:13:31,018 --> 00:13:32,561
Okey. Selamat malam.

218
00:13:33,145 --> 00:13:33,979
Tidurlah.

219
00:13:36,106 --> 00:13:38,818
Sudah lama tak minum sama.
Seronok rasanya.

220
00:13:49,286 --> 00:13:52,790
PANGGILAN MASUK

221
00:13:58,337 --> 00:13:59,171
Wanita?

222
00:13:59,755 --> 00:14:00,589
Ya.

223
00:14:01,131 --> 00:14:02,925
Siapa yang telefon tengah malam?

224
00:14:07,221 --> 00:14:08,055
Cakaplah.

225
00:14:10,766 --> 00:14:11,600
Yang-jung.

226
00:14:14,478 --> 00:14:15,521
Saya bakal jadi ayah.

227
00:14:17,523 --> 00:14:18,524
Bila?

228
00:14:19,108 --> 00:14:20,943
Lagi dua bulan. Anak perempuan.

229
00:14:23,612 --> 00:14:25,698
Sudah tiga tahun kami bersama.

230
00:14:26,824 --> 00:14:30,077
Hei, awak patut beritahu saya
jika awak dah berkeluarga!

231
00:14:30,160 --> 00:14:32,746
Awak takkan benarkan saya turut serta.

232
00:14:36,750 --> 00:14:38,586
Pergi balik. Saya akan uruskan.

233
00:14:38,669 --> 00:14:40,963
Tak nak, dah lama tak minum sama.

234
00:14:41,046 --> 00:14:42,131
Saya takkan balik.

235
00:14:42,214 --> 00:14:43,632
Pergi balik.

236
00:14:44,592 --> 00:14:46,093
Panas baran betul.

237
00:14:49,054 --> 00:14:49,889
Nah.

238
00:14:50,973 --> 00:14:52,266
Tak perlulah.

239
00:14:52,766 --> 00:14:55,352
Bukan untuk awak.
Beli daging untuk isteri awak.

240
00:14:55,436 --> 00:14:57,980
Zat besi penting
untuk wanita mengandung. Nah.

241
00:15:00,399 --> 00:15:01,734
Kenapa banyak sangat?

242
00:15:05,195 --> 00:15:06,113
Lama lagi?

243
00:15:06,196 --> 00:15:07,323
Tak, sekejap.

244
00:15:07,406 --> 00:15:09,116
- Baiklah. Saya turun.
- Okey.

245
00:15:11,994 --> 00:15:13,078
Panggil teksi.

246
00:15:13,162 --> 00:15:15,414
Saya hisap rokok sementara awak menunggu.

247
00:15:17,374 --> 00:15:18,208
Yang-jung.

248
00:15:21,795 --> 00:15:22,630
Terima kasih.

249
00:15:24,131 --> 00:15:25,466
Jangan mengarut.

250
00:15:28,719 --> 00:15:30,512
Awak memang terbaik.

251
00:15:31,180 --> 00:15:33,182
Saya akan belikan daging hanwoo.

252
00:15:38,687 --> 00:15:40,397
Hyeon-ju masuk tidur dulu.

253
00:15:40,898 --> 00:15:41,732
Okey.

254
00:15:44,193 --> 00:15:45,027
Awak okey?

255
00:15:45,110 --> 00:15:45,986
Ya.

256
00:15:53,702 --> 00:15:55,496
Tentu tuan sangat risau.

257
00:15:56,163 --> 00:15:59,291
Saya yang ajar Myeong-gil.
Dia tanggungjawab saya.

258
00:16:00,334 --> 00:16:02,127
Tapi dengan badan begini,

259
00:16:02,920 --> 00:16:04,296
saya hilang keberanian

260
00:16:05,756 --> 00:16:06,674
untuk berlawan.

261
00:16:09,426 --> 00:16:10,803
Saya cuma mampu

262
00:16:11,887 --> 00:16:14,848
menjaga Hyeon-ju. Itu sahaja.

263
00:17:25,669 --> 00:17:26,795
Encik siapa?

264
00:17:27,713 --> 00:17:28,547
Saya…

265
00:17:29,673 --> 00:17:30,507
Pak cik

266
00:17:32,259 --> 00:17:33,218
kawan ayah awak.

267
00:17:38,682 --> 00:17:41,351
Jangan menangis.

268
00:17:41,435 --> 00:17:42,269
Jangan menangis.

269
00:17:43,729 --> 00:17:44,897
Aduhai.

270
00:17:46,482 --> 00:17:48,484
Ayah!

271
00:17:53,280 --> 00:17:56,617
TAKZIAH

272
00:17:57,576 --> 00:17:58,619
Apa maksud awak?

273
00:18:01,371 --> 00:18:02,831
Penuhkan koridor ini

274
00:18:03,415 --> 00:18:04,666
dengan bunga paling mahal.

275
00:18:05,209 --> 00:18:06,043
Baiklah.

276
00:18:06,126 --> 00:18:09,546
Suruh sepuluh orang berkawal
hingga upacara selesai.

277
00:18:10,255 --> 00:18:11,215
Bersenjata?

278
00:18:11,298 --> 00:18:12,132
Usah.

279
00:18:12,633 --> 00:18:14,843
Budak itu bersendirian di dalam.

280
00:18:14,927 --> 00:18:16,178
Pastikan dia makan.

281
00:18:16,261 --> 00:18:17,096
Baiklah.

282
00:18:18,639 --> 00:18:21,350
Bos, awak mungkin tertinggal
skarf di dalam.

283
00:18:21,433 --> 00:18:22,768
Tak apa. Biarkan.

284
00:18:25,395 --> 00:18:27,106
Tapi, kenapa dia bunuh diri?

285
00:18:28,232 --> 00:18:29,399
Pagi hantar akhbar,

286
00:18:29,483 --> 00:18:32,361
siang hari dia di kilang,
malam jadi pemandu.

287
00:18:32,861 --> 00:18:36,406
Dua tahun dia bekerja siang malam
untuk selamatkan anak dia.

288
00:18:36,490 --> 00:18:37,950
Tidur tiga jam sahaja.

289
00:18:38,492 --> 00:18:40,577
Anak dia dah sihat. Kenapa bunuh diri?

290
00:18:41,703 --> 00:18:42,788
Tiada sebab.

291
00:18:43,705 --> 00:18:45,082
Duit yang dia pinjam,

292
00:18:45,165 --> 00:18:47,376
saya tak kenakan kadar bunga.

293
00:18:48,127 --> 00:18:50,879
Jika perlu, saya turut tawar
untuk lanjutkan tempoh.

294
00:18:59,471 --> 00:19:00,347
Saya akan siasat.

295
00:19:00,931 --> 00:19:02,141
Saya tak faham.

296
00:19:10,524 --> 00:19:11,358
Di sana.

297
00:19:15,946 --> 00:19:16,780
Tingkat tiga.

298
00:19:26,039 --> 00:19:26,874
Maaf.

299
00:19:29,126 --> 00:19:29,960
Aduhai.

300
00:19:30,544 --> 00:19:33,505
Awak ingin ke upacara pengebumian
En. Cha Sang-ho?

301
00:19:35,174 --> 00:19:36,008
Ya.

302
00:19:39,678 --> 00:19:43,182
Dua tahun lalu, saya dibedah
dan tak boleh angkat barang berat.

303
00:19:44,057 --> 00:19:46,518
Ayah Hyeon-ju tolong saya buang sampah

304
00:19:46,602 --> 00:19:48,312
selama tiga bulan.

305
00:19:49,855 --> 00:19:54,443
Aduhai. Dia orang
yang sangat baik dan rajin.

306
00:19:55,944 --> 00:19:57,696
Anak dia, Hyeon-ju…

307
00:19:58,238 --> 00:20:01,450
Dia sakit dan tiada ibu untuk menjaga dia.

308
00:20:01,533 --> 00:20:04,745
Jadi saya beri dia makan
dan sediakan lauk-pauk

309
00:20:05,329 --> 00:20:07,206
agar mereka ada makanan.

310
00:20:07,289 --> 00:20:08,415
Hyeon-ju dah sihat,

311
00:20:09,041 --> 00:20:11,168
jadi kenapa dia bunuh diri?

312
00:20:11,251 --> 00:20:14,421
Semuanya kerana lintah darat tak guna itu!

313
00:20:15,172 --> 00:20:17,925
Aduhai. Mereka datang sesuka hati,

314
00:20:18,008 --> 00:20:21,720
mengugut dan belasah dia. Dahsyat sungguh.

315
00:20:22,221 --> 00:20:23,096
Ingat muka mereka?

316
00:20:24,848 --> 00:20:25,682
Seorang

317
00:20:26,225 --> 00:20:27,809
badan besar macam beruang.

318
00:20:28,393 --> 00:20:30,938
Seorang lagi sangat tinggi.

319
00:20:34,149 --> 00:20:35,359
Sebulan kemudian,

320
00:20:35,984 --> 00:20:39,238
seorang lagi peminjam bunuh diri.

321
00:20:40,113 --> 00:20:41,740
Ahli keluarga dia sakit,

322
00:20:41,823 --> 00:20:44,534
jadi saya beri pinjaman tanpa kadar bunga.

323
00:20:46,245 --> 00:20:47,621
Saya balik awal sangat.

324
00:20:50,165 --> 00:20:50,999
Tengok tangga.

325
00:20:55,545 --> 00:20:56,546
Yang-jung.

326
00:21:03,220 --> 00:21:04,054
Saya balik.

327
00:21:05,472 --> 00:21:06,306
Baliklah.

328
00:21:06,390 --> 00:21:07,224
Okey.

329
00:21:09,059 --> 00:21:10,060
Selamat malam.

330
00:21:16,358 --> 00:21:18,151
Yang-jung dapat tahu,

331
00:21:18,777 --> 00:21:20,988
mereka yang terima pinjaman

332
00:21:21,071 --> 00:21:23,490
untuk merawat ahli keluarga yang sakit

333
00:21:25,367 --> 00:21:26,952
dilawati oleh Myeong-gil.

334
00:21:27,494 --> 00:21:29,454
Dia peras beberapa juta sebulan,

335
00:21:29,538 --> 00:21:31,915
kononnya yuran lanjutan pinjaman

336
00:21:33,208 --> 00:21:35,711
dengan alasan arahan daripada saya.

337
00:21:37,004 --> 00:21:40,132
Ibu saya terperdaya
dengan helah yang sama.

338
00:21:41,967 --> 00:21:44,177
Ia disertakan dalam kontrak.

339
00:21:47,139 --> 00:21:48,098
Ah…

340
00:21:49,891 --> 00:21:50,726
Maaf.

341
00:21:51,810 --> 00:21:52,686
Tak.

342
00:21:52,769 --> 00:21:55,856
Ramai jadi mangsa kerana saya.

343
00:21:56,648 --> 00:21:57,482
Tak.

344
00:21:58,734 --> 00:22:01,320
Tuan tak perlu minta maaf.

345
00:22:01,945 --> 00:22:04,197
Tuan terlalu bertanggungjawab,

346
00:22:04,281 --> 00:22:07,284
sebab itu juga tuan rasa amat bersalah.

347
00:22:08,035 --> 00:22:10,495
Orang kejam sahaja tak rasa bersalah.

348
00:22:11,413 --> 00:22:12,914
Mereka salahkan orang lain

349
00:22:13,498 --> 00:22:15,167
dan buli orang yang lemah.

350
00:22:17,252 --> 00:22:19,838
Saya percaya, kami semua berkumpul di sini

351
00:22:19,921 --> 00:22:22,215
kerana kebaikan yang tuan pamerkan.

352
00:22:22,799 --> 00:22:23,633
Hyeon-ju

353
00:22:24,301 --> 00:22:28,013
mungkin tak tahu tuan beli
rumah anak yatim itu kerana dia,

354
00:22:28,638 --> 00:22:30,891
tapi dia percaya sepenuhnya kepada tuan.

355
00:22:32,017 --> 00:22:35,103
Kita pasti akan tumpaskan Kim Myeong-gil.

356
00:22:35,854 --> 00:22:37,230
Jangan salahkan diri tuan.

357
00:22:39,232 --> 00:22:40,859
Tolong jaga kesihatan tuan.

358
00:22:55,165 --> 00:22:56,375
Selepas hal ini tamat,

359
00:22:57,250 --> 00:22:59,836
saya akan sediakan gim tinju peribadi

360
00:22:59,920 --> 00:23:01,421
supaya awak boleh fokus

361
00:23:01,505 --> 00:23:04,049
dan berlatih sehingga awak jadi juara.

362
00:23:04,841 --> 00:23:06,385
Di tingkat satu gim itu,

363
00:23:06,468 --> 00:23:08,804
saya akan sediakan kafe untuk ibu awak.

364
00:23:09,971 --> 00:23:11,640
Sewa percuma selagi saya hidup.

365
00:23:18,313 --> 00:23:20,273
Awak tergamam?

366
00:23:20,357 --> 00:23:21,191
Ya.

367
00:23:23,360 --> 00:23:24,736
Ucaplah terima kasih.

368
00:23:26,154 --> 00:23:26,988
Oh…

369
00:23:28,115 --> 00:23:29,533
Terima kasih, tuan.

370
00:23:29,616 --> 00:23:30,450
Tak.

371
00:23:32,702 --> 00:23:34,204
Terima kasih kepada awak.

372
00:23:36,331 --> 00:23:38,458
Awak ajar saya tentang kemudaan.

373
00:23:41,044 --> 00:23:41,878
Inilah

374
00:23:43,463 --> 00:23:44,631
"flex!"

375
00:23:46,466 --> 00:23:47,467
Macam mana?

376
00:23:47,551 --> 00:23:48,510
Ya.

377
00:23:53,765 --> 00:23:54,599
Tengok situ.

378
00:23:54,683 --> 00:23:56,518
- Sini?
- Tak, sebelah sana.

379
00:23:56,601 --> 00:23:57,436
Baiklah.

380
00:24:14,161 --> 00:24:15,078
Bahagian itu pula?

381
00:24:15,162 --> 00:24:16,288
Baiklah.

382
00:24:27,215 --> 00:24:29,217
SPEC ACE

383
00:24:30,802 --> 00:24:31,636
Terima kasih.

384
00:24:31,720 --> 00:24:33,013
- Sama-sama.
- Teruskan.

385
00:24:47,319 --> 00:24:48,695
GANG-YONG

386
00:24:50,322 --> 00:24:51,156
Ya.

387
00:24:51,239 --> 00:24:52,824
Onyu-ro 88.

388
00:24:53,909 --> 00:24:54,784
Puas hati?

389
00:24:55,911 --> 00:24:56,828
Terima kasih.

390
00:25:08,298 --> 00:25:09,883
- Jom.
- Baiklah!

391
00:26:24,416 --> 00:26:25,417
Berhenti!

392
00:26:29,963 --> 00:26:31,715
Nampaknya Presiden Choi bertongkat?

393
00:26:46,771 --> 00:26:47,897
Teknik air garam.

394
00:26:50,609 --> 00:26:51,776
Jang-do dah buka mulut?

395
00:26:52,444 --> 00:26:53,737
Saya tak tahu.

396
00:26:56,615 --> 00:26:59,284
Lebih selamat jika anggap
dia dah buka mulut.

397
00:27:00,493 --> 00:27:01,828
Bunuh Presiden Choi…

398
00:27:04,289 --> 00:27:05,332
kemudian, dia.

399
00:27:06,499 --> 00:27:07,542
Baiklah.

400
00:27:12,631 --> 00:27:13,465
Tuan!

401
00:27:18,887 --> 00:27:21,056
LEE DU-YEONG

402
00:27:30,106 --> 00:27:31,775
Sabar dan jangan bunuh dia.

403
00:27:32,651 --> 00:27:34,027
Saya nak tanya sesuatu.

404
00:27:34,110 --> 00:27:34,944
Baiklah.

405
00:27:35,612 --> 00:27:36,988
Tanggalkan itu dulu.

406
00:27:37,072 --> 00:27:37,906
Baiklah.

407
00:28:07,769 --> 00:28:08,603
Du-yeong.

408
00:28:10,313 --> 00:28:11,564
Ada orang datang.

409
00:28:28,081 --> 00:28:29,332
Siapa?

410
00:28:29,416 --> 00:28:31,459
Maaf, saya jiran tingkat bawah.

411
00:28:31,543 --> 00:28:33,086
Air bocor dari siling.

412
00:28:33,962 --> 00:28:36,089
Boleh saya periksa bilik air awak?

413
00:28:40,760 --> 00:28:41,761
Sekejap sahaja.

414
00:28:41,845 --> 00:28:43,388
Rumah kami dibanjiri air.

415
00:28:44,848 --> 00:28:46,182
Anak-anak tak boleh tidur.

416
00:28:48,977 --> 00:28:50,019
Tolong beri kerjasama.

417
00:28:53,398 --> 00:28:54,482
Sekarang?

418
00:28:54,566 --> 00:28:56,109
Ya, sekejap sahaja.

419
00:28:56,985 --> 00:28:58,194
Saya periksa sahaja.

420
00:29:12,167 --> 00:29:13,001
Sayang?

421
00:29:13,752 --> 00:29:14,586
Ya.

422
00:29:16,755 --> 00:29:17,589
Siapa?

423
00:29:18,173 --> 00:29:19,841
Jiran bawah. Dia kata siling bocor.

424
00:29:23,428 --> 00:29:24,512
- Beralih.
- Apa?

425
00:29:24,596 --> 00:29:25,430
Beralih.

426
00:29:31,186 --> 00:29:32,395
Diam.

427
00:29:39,194 --> 00:29:40,236
- Tunggu.
- Okey.

428
00:29:55,376 --> 00:29:56,211
Sayang.

429
00:29:56,294 --> 00:29:59,047
Telefon polis, kata ada rompakan.

430
00:29:59,839 --> 00:30:00,882
Kenapa?

431
00:30:00,965 --> 00:30:02,300
Nanti saya terangkan.

432
00:30:03,176 --> 00:30:04,010
Percaya saya, kan?

433
00:30:05,136 --> 00:30:06,679
- Ya.
- Dan

434
00:30:07,889 --> 00:30:08,973
apa pun terjadi,

435
00:30:10,600 --> 00:30:12,268
jangan buka pintu.

436
00:30:12,352 --> 00:30:13,186
Okey.

437
00:30:15,563 --> 00:30:16,523
Okey.

438
00:30:16,606 --> 00:30:18,775
Jangan risau, sayang.

439
00:30:18,858 --> 00:30:20,360
Semua akan okey. Tak apa.

440
00:30:25,365 --> 00:30:26,574
Aduhai.

441
00:30:49,848 --> 00:30:52,392
Dongjak-gu, Samjin-dong.

442
00:31:06,698 --> 00:31:10,159
Tolong datang cepat.
Suami saya dalam bahaya.

443
00:31:21,129 --> 00:31:23,047
Hei, masuk cepat.

444
00:31:23,131 --> 00:31:24,048
Heret dia keluar.

445
00:31:26,885 --> 00:31:28,303
Apa ini? Celaka!

446
00:31:29,512 --> 00:31:30,805
Cis.

447
00:31:32,181 --> 00:31:35,101
Cis. Jahanam!

448
00:31:36,978 --> 00:31:39,105
Jahanam!

449
00:31:56,205 --> 00:31:58,541
Bedebah!

450
00:32:01,544 --> 00:32:02,378
Cis!

451
00:32:05,673 --> 00:32:06,883
Celaka!

452
00:33:21,708 --> 00:33:23,751
Beritahu lokasi Hwang Yang-jung,

453
00:33:25,169 --> 00:33:26,671
isteri kau akan selamat.

454
00:33:31,300 --> 00:33:32,677
Aku tak pernah

455
00:33:34,137 --> 00:33:35,138
mungkir janji.

456
00:33:41,644 --> 00:33:42,478
Percayalah.

457
00:34:13,301 --> 00:34:14,927
- Tuan dah bangun?
- Ya.

458
00:34:16,721 --> 00:34:17,722
Selamat pagi.

459
00:34:17,805 --> 00:34:19,182
- Dah bangun?
- Ya.

460
00:34:22,060 --> 00:34:22,894
Duduklah.

461
00:34:26,564 --> 00:34:28,274
Rumah ini riuh-rendah.

462
00:34:28,983 --> 00:34:30,985
Ya, kita makan beramai-ramai.

463
00:34:32,361 --> 00:34:34,864
Woo-jin, bangun. Jom sarapan.

464
00:34:38,367 --> 00:34:40,787
- Terima kasih banyak.
- Tak susah pun.

465
00:34:43,289 --> 00:34:44,874
- Dia tak nak makan?
- Masih tidur.

466
00:34:45,458 --> 00:34:47,668
Suruhlah dia sambung tidur selepas makan.

467
00:34:48,252 --> 00:34:49,629
Dia mabuk teruk, bukan?

468
00:34:49,712 --> 00:34:50,922
Ya.

469
00:34:51,005 --> 00:34:52,715
Tak pernah mabuk konon.

470
00:34:54,634 --> 00:34:55,635
Mari makan.

471
00:34:55,718 --> 00:34:58,262
- Mari makan.
- Mari makan.

472
00:35:09,482 --> 00:35:11,067
- Gun-woo.
- Ya.

473
00:35:11,150 --> 00:35:13,486
Bila awak akan hantar ibu awak?

474
00:35:14,028 --> 00:35:16,531
Biar saya hantar. Pinjamkan kereta datuk.

475
00:35:17,115 --> 00:35:20,076
Kereta itu dah lama terbiar.
Mungkin bahaya. Berhati-hati.

476
00:35:20,159 --> 00:35:21,369
- Okey.
- Bagus.

477
00:35:21,869 --> 00:35:24,956
Kita pergi selepas sarapan?
Sejam sahaja dari sini.

478
00:35:26,624 --> 00:35:27,542
Mak, boleh?

479
00:35:27,625 --> 00:35:29,168
Saya rasa,

480
00:35:29,836 --> 00:35:32,463
saya lebih selesa tinggal di sini

481
00:35:32,547 --> 00:35:34,715
sambil memasak untuk semua orang.

482
00:35:37,802 --> 00:35:38,636
Puan.

483
00:35:40,054 --> 00:35:42,140
Saya harap saya tak menyusahkan,

484
00:35:43,099 --> 00:35:45,476
tapi apa kata awak bantu rumah anak yatim?

485
00:35:47,395 --> 00:35:50,064
Kemahiran memasak awak sangat hebat.

486
00:35:50,648 --> 00:35:52,650
Tentu anak-anak di sana akan suka.

487
00:35:54,569 --> 00:35:57,029
Masakan ni memang sedap.

488
00:36:01,367 --> 00:36:03,244
Mak, saya rasa itu idea bernas.

489
00:36:05,705 --> 00:36:06,539
Aduhai.

490
00:36:08,249 --> 00:36:10,251
Baiklah, jika saya boleh membantu.

491
00:36:10,334 --> 00:36:11,377
Terima kasih.

492
00:36:13,296 --> 00:36:14,130
Okey.

493
00:36:26,851 --> 00:36:28,269
Kita tinggal berasingan.

494
00:36:28,853 --> 00:36:30,688
Janji awak akan jaga makan?

495
00:36:31,772 --> 00:36:32,607
Ya.

496
00:36:40,323 --> 00:36:41,699
Sentiasa jaga diri.

497
00:36:44,035 --> 00:36:44,869
Okey.

498
00:36:50,499 --> 00:36:51,584
Jangan risau.

499
00:36:55,504 --> 00:36:57,590
- Mak percayakan anak mak.
- Okey.

500
00:37:18,236 --> 00:37:21,030
HWANGSUSA

501
00:37:30,039 --> 00:37:31,916
SISTEM KESELAMATAN DIPADAM

502
00:37:35,795 --> 00:37:36,629
Min-dong.

503
00:38:28,264 --> 00:38:29,765
Macam mana kau jumpa aku?

504
00:38:30,599 --> 00:38:31,434
Mudah.

505
00:38:32,685 --> 00:38:34,520
Lee Du-yeong yang beritahu.

506
00:38:37,440 --> 00:38:38,816
Kau apa-apakan isteri dia?

507
00:38:40,151 --> 00:38:41,027
Wah.

508
00:38:43,779 --> 00:38:44,655
Kau bunuh mereka?

